  "description": [
    "LYON COUNTY TIMES YBRING TON NEVADA Saturday December 7 1901 The Bluestone mine was closed down yesterday and all the em ployes discharged Work has been suspended in definitely in the Bluestone copper mine near Yerington Lyon coun ty We do not know where the two above items originated but they have been going the rounds of the State press for the past week and are damnable lies From the time the Excelsior Company closed the Bluestone smelter last August the outside press seems to have deter mined to give this property a black eye Columns of stuff have been published which have contained not the slightest particle of truth and the lying has become so gen eral that one is almost led to be lieve that there is concert of act ion by outsiders and possibly some insiders to injure this camp No such items as the two above cited ever appeared in the Times but we have published the facts in re gard to the Bluestone and other mining prospects in this section and if our exchanges would look over our columns they would not get so horribly twisted up on min ing news from this section It"
  ],
